  "subject": "Upgrade UI tests selenium in a new module",
  "commit_message": "Upgrade UI tests selenium in a new module\n\nIsolates the onapUiSanity suite code in a new module, so selenium could\nbe updated without affecting other suites or test cases.\nUpgrade selenium version from 2.53.1 to 3.141.59. Along with, updates\nfirefox and uses the geckodriver required to operate modern firefox\nbrowsers.\nCreates a new docker image to run the new suite.\n\nChange-Id: Iaa8d6e61dfb5d866257dc95cf649077b68fe85ed\nIssue-ID: SDC-2688\nSigned-off-by: andre.schmid <andre.schmid@est.tech>\n",
